      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While it currently runs, the transmission is slipping significantly, and there are several major oil leaks that will require immediate attention. The body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn with non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a donor vehicle for parts, but it is not currently reliable for daily transportation.",
